ComicInfo.Summary: "Bad Moon Rising" Part 2 of 2, The GI Joe team is under fire from all sides: Cobra, The Coil, The Jugglers...and now the public! As the administration hangs our heroes out to dry, Cobra pounds the final nail in the coffin. It's wall-to-wall action and backstabbing evil as Destro rises to power... only to find a big surprise waiting for him when he reaches his goal. All this and the conclusion of the Snake-Eyes/Wraith showdown in "Bad Moon Rising" Part 2!
